title: Grateful Dead Live at Park West Ski Resort on 1987-08-20
lineage: Master cassettes (Nakamichi DR-1) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.6 MHz)> dBpoweramp (24/96) > Adobe Audition CC 2020 > TLH flac2496
description:
Set I
The Addams Family
Big Boss Man >
Promised Land
Dire Wolf
New Minglewood Blues
Row Jimmy
It's All Over Now
Loser
Cassidy
When Push Comes To Shove
Set II
China Cat Sunflower >
I Know You Rider
Man Smart (Woman Smarter)
Ship Of Fools
Truckin' >
Smokestack Lightning >
Drums >
Space >
The Wheel >
Gimme Some Lovin' >
All Along The Watchtower >
Stella Blue >
Sugar Magnolia

Encore:
The Mighty Quinn (Quinn The Eskimo)


Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums

reviews.review_text: One day Hey Matt one day behind you. Please keep it up these archives are truly priceless and appreciated. Peace.Mike
new source the sound on this is amazing. I was at this show and have had an old cassette for 30 years. What a treat this recording is.
